Ibyago byo kwibasirwa n'indwara ya Coronavirus (COVID-19) byiyongera cyane muri EU/Economic Region of Europe na UK, kuva ku itariki ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020
Ibikorwa by'ubwandu bwa Coronavirus (COVID-19) bigaragaza ko hari ibintu bisa n'ibyo mu bihugu by'umuryango w'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza, bikaba byemeza ko nubwo ibipimo byabyo bitandukanye bitewe n'ibihugu, icyorezo cya COVID-19 kigenda gitera imbere mu buryo bwihuse mu bihugu byose.
Dukurikije ibyabaye mu Butaliyani, ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi ba COVID-19 bigomba kurushaho kwitegura ko hazabaho uburwayi bwinshi bukeneye kwitabwaho, cyane cyane mu buryo bukomeye.
Ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, hari umubare munini w'abantu banduye indwara ya PN na ETIOLOGIE bataramenyekana, bagaragaye mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Ku itariki ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'Ubushinwa gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara cyatangaje ko ikigeragezo cy'iyi ndwara ari coronavirus nshya ubu yitwa coronavirus syndrome respiratoire acute grave 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Kuva icyo gihe, indwara ziterwa n'ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 ziswe indwara ya coronavirus (COVID-19).
Ubuhamya bugaragaza ko abagera kuri 80% by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 baba bafite indwara yoroheje, ari yo ndwara y'imyenda yo mu mwuka ifite cyangwa idafite pneumonia, kandi abenshi muri bo barakira.
Mu bantu bagera kuri 14%, COVID-19 igenda ihinduka indwara ikomeye cyane igasaba kuvurirwa mu bitaro, mu gihe abandi 6% baba bafite indwara ikomeye igasaba kwivuza cyane.
Urupfu rw'abarwayi bavurirwa mu bitaro kubera COVID-19 ni 4%.
Muri iki cyifuzo, twasuzumye uko COVID-19 yibasiye ibihugu by'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Afurika y'u Burayi/Afurika y'Ubukungu (EU/EEA) n'u Bwongereza, maze tugereranya n'ibyabaye mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Nanone twagereranyije umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 muri EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza n'uw'abanduye mu Butaliyani kuva ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 mu bihugu by'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/EEA no mu Bwongereza
Nyuma y'u Bushinwa, COVID-19 yagwiriye mu by'ubutaka ndetse n'ibindi bice by'isi byakurikiyeho icyorezo cy'indwara ya COVID-19.
Ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe 2020, Umuyobozi Mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo.
Mu kinyamakuru cya Eurosurveillance 2020 cyo ku itariki ya 5 Werurwe, Spiteri et al. batangaje ko ari we muntu wa mbere w'i Burayi wemejwe ko afite icyorezo cya COVID-19 hashingiwe ku bisobanuro byatanzwe na OMS.
Mu bihugu by'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/EEA, abantu batatu ba mbere bemejwe ko banduye, bavuzwe n'Ubufaransa ku wa 24 Mutarama 2020 mu bantu bagarutse bavuye i Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020, COVID-19 imaze kwandura mu bihugu 30 by'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ibihugu by'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/EEA no mu Bwongereza (Ubwongereza), hagati y'itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 na 15 Werurwe 2020 by'aho hakaba harimo, hari abantu 39,768 banduye n'abapfuye 1,727 bagaragaye, hamwe n'abantu 17,750 banduye n'abapfuye 1,441 bo mu Butaliyani gusa.
