Ibi byatangajwe mu rwego rwo gusuzuma uko COVID-19 igenda mu bihugu by'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/EEA no mu Bwongereza, ndetse no kugereranya uko igenda mu Butaliyani.
