Nyamara, COVID-19 ifite igipimo cyo hasi cy'uburwayi n'urupfu ugereranyije na SARS, ariko ikwirakwira cyane kandi igakwira abantu bakuru kurusha abakiri bato, ndetse ikagira ingaruka nyinshi ku bagabo kurusha ku bagore.
Mu rwego rwo gusubiza ku mubare w'ibitabo byihuta ku birebana n'iyo ndwara ivutse, iyi ngingo yagerageje gutanga ibisobanuro ku buryo bwimbitse kandi ku buryo bwimbitse ku birebana n'ubushakashatsi bukomeje kwiyongera.
Tuzasuzuma ibintu by'ibanze byerekeye indwara, uburwayi, virusi, indwara, uburyo bwo kuzirwanya, ibipimo by'indwara n'ubudahangarwa.
Nubwo hari ibibazo byinshi bitarabonerwa ibisubizo, twizeye ko iki cyifuzo kizatuma dusobanukirwa neza icyo kibazo cy'indwara ziteye ubwoba.
Umunsi mukuru wa Spring Festival ku wa 25 Mutarama 2020 wabaye umunsi w'ingenzi kandi utazibagirana ku Bashinwa bose bategetswe kuguma mu rugo mu gihe cy'ibiruhuko no mu byumweru bikurikiyeho kubera icyorezo cy'indwara nshya ya virusi.
Iyi virusi ni kimwe cyane na coronavirus (CoV) yateje icyorezo cy'indwara y'ubuhumekero bukomeye (SARS) mu mwaka wa 2003; ni yo mpamvu iyi virusi yiswe SARS-CoV-2 na World Health Organisation (WHO) ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, kandi indwara yateje yitwa CoV Disease-19 (COVID-19).
Iki cyorezo cyatangiye mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa, maze gitangira gukwirakwira mu gihugu hose no mu bindi bihugu hafi 50 ku isi hose.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 2 Werurwe 2020, iyi virusi imaze gutuma haboneka abantu 80,000 banduye COVID-19, abagera kuri 40,000 bagasubizwa mu rugo, abagera ku 3,000 bagapfa.
OMS iragabisha ko COVID-19 ari umwanzi w'abaturage wa 1 kandi ko ishobora guteza akaga gakomeye kurusha iterabwoba.
Dukurikije PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), mu gihe kitageze ku mezi abiri uhereye ku nkuru ya mbere yo ku itariki ya 7 Mutarama 2020 yashyizeho urutonde rw'indwara yiherereye ku barwayi bamwe na bamwe, hasohotse ibitabo birenga 200 ku COVID-19, birimo viroloji, epidemiologie, etiologie, diagnosis, n'ubuvuzi.
Iyi raporo igamije gusobanura uko ubushakashatsi bwateye imbere muri iki gisata gishya gikorerwamo n'abantu benshi.
Mu gihe bishoboka, tugerageza kugereranya COVID-19 na SARS n'indi ndwara iterwa na CoV, ari yo syndrome respiratoire yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS, icyorezo cyo mu mwaka wa 2012).
Nanone tuzasuzuma ibyo twamaze kwiga ku birebana no kwirinda indwara no kuzivura, hamwe n'ibindi bibazo byinshi bitarabonerwa ibisubizo, ariko byihutirwa.
Mu mico ya kera, CoV ifatwa nk'ikigeragezo kitandura ku bantu, cyane cyane iyo ituma abantu bagera kuri 15% bahura n'indwara y'ibicurane 4.
Nyamara muri iki kinyejana, twabonye ko COVID-19 ishobora gutera indwara nyinshi mu bantu inshuro ebyiri ari yo SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, buri kimwe cyateje icyorezo cyatangiriye mu Bushinwa mu 2003 na Arabiya Sawudite mu 2012, kandi cyahise gikwira mu bindi bihugu byinshi, cyateje ubwandu n'urupfu bikabije.
Kubera iyo mpamvu, COVID-19 ubu ni icyorezo cya gatatu cya CoV mu mateka y'abantu.
Nk'uko bigaragara mu Gashyantare 1.1, icyorezo cy'indwara y'ubwonko cy'inkomoko itaramenyekana cyatangajwe bwa mbere mu mujyi wa Wuhan ku wa 31 Ukuboza 2019 ku Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima ya Repubulika y'u Bushinwa.
Nyuma y'iminsi irindwi, ikoranabuhanga rya CoV ryatangiye gukora.
Ku itariki ya 15 Mutarama 2020, havuzwe icyorezo cya Wuhan cya mbere.
Hagati aho, icyorezo cyakwirakwiriye mu migi, mu ntara no mu bihugu by'abaturanyi.
Ku itariki ya 20 Mutarama, havuzwe ko hari ubwandu bw'abatanga ubuvuzi, ibyo bikaba byumvikanisha ko umuntu ashobora kwandura indwara.
Ku itariki ya 23 Mutarama, icyorezo cy'ibicurane cy'akarere cyatangiye mu mujyi wa Wuhan, maze imodoka zose zitwara abantu zihagarara.
Ku itariki ya 24 Mutarama, ikigo cya mbere cy'ubuvuzi cyatangaje ko mu bantu 41 banduye iki cyorezo, 21 gusa ari bo bagiranye na Wuhan isoko ry'ibiribwa byo mu nyanja, aho indwara y'iyo ndwara yavuye ku nyamaswa zitamenyekanye.
Ku itariki ya 30 Mutarama, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari imimerere y'ubukungu ku isi hose.
Igihe iyi nkuru yandikwaga, iyo ndwara yari imaze gukwira mu Bushinwa hose no mu bindi bihugu hafi 50 byo hirya no hino ku isi. - Abaheburayo 2:2.
Kubera ko ibintu bigenda byihuta cyane, icyorezo kigomba kurangira kandi kikagira imbaraga nyinshi.
Ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'ibiro byinshi ku barwayi 8,866, bugizwe n'abarwayi 4,021 banduye COVID-19, bwatanze ibi bisobanuro bikurikira by'icyorezo (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
