Bivugwa ko SARS-CoV-2 ifite ubukana bw'imirasire y'ibirahuri n'ubushyuhe ku 56 °C mu gihe cy'iminota 30; ether, ethanol 75%, disinfectants irimo klorini, acide perasate, chloroform, n'ibindi bivamo ibinure, ariko atari chlorhexidin, bikora neza mu guhagarika virusi.
