Coronavirus (CoV) ni virusi yo mu muryango wa Coronaviridae, igizwe n'itsinda ry'indwara z'ubwonko, zifite intumbero nziza, kandi zifite intambwe imwe.
Iyi virusi ifite genom nini cyane ifite uburebure bwa 26 kugeza 32 kilobase mu virusi ya RNA yitwa "CoV", kubera ko ifite imiterere isa n'iy'ikamba munsi ya microscope ya elegitoroni.
Kubera ko CoV ifite imiterere y'ibinyabuzima bitandukanye, nta moko yayo ari mu bice by'ibinyabuzima by'ibinyabuzima.
