Iyo poroteyine ikora ibindi bintu kugira ngo ibe poroteyine 16 zitari iz'ubwubatsi, zitwa nsp1~16.
Ibisigaye by'ubwoko bw'ibinyabuzima bikubiyemo ingengabihe y'ubumenyi bwuguruye (ORF) ku birebana n'imiterere y'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima, harimo intambwe cyangwa igitereko (S), uruhu cyangwa igitereko (E), uruhu (M), n'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima byitwa nucleoproteins (N).
Hari kandi poroteyine z'inyongera zigenewe ubwoko runaka bw'ibinyabuzima, kandi zikwandikwa n'ibinyabuzima bitandukanye by'ibinyabuzima by'ibinyabuzima by'ibinyabuzima by'ibinyabuzima.
Dukurikije itandukaniro ku cyiciro cy'ibinyabuzima, CoV yashyizwe mu matsinda ane (alpha-CoV, beta-CoV, gamma-CoV, na delta-CoV); muri ayo matsinda ane, beta-CoV ifite umubare munini w'abantu bafite HCoV kandi igabanyirizwa mu matsinda ane (A, B, C, na D).
Ibimenyetso bya phylogenetic bigaragaza ko ibishwi n'ibikoko by'ibishwi ari byo bikomoka ku ngirabuzimafatizo nyinshi za alpha-CoV na beta-CoV, mu gihe inkoko ari zo zikomoka ku mazi akomeye ya gamma-CoV na delta-CoV.
