Mu kwezi kwa cumi na kabiri 2019, coronavirus nshya ya 2019 (2019-nCoV) yatumye habaho icyorezo, ubu cyitwa indwara ya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) kandi iyi virusi yiswe coronavirus syndrome respiratoire acute grave 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
