Taiwan yateye imbere mu gukora mask zo mu maso kandi igahana abakiga ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi.Ibigereranyo byakozwe ku Bwongereza no muri Amerika bigaragaza ko kugabanya (guceceka, ariko ntibuhagarike ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo) no kugabanya (guhagarika ukwiyongera kw'icyorezo) bifite imbogamizi zikomeye.
Gushyiraho politiki nziza yo kugabanya umubare munini w'abantu bifuza ubuvuzi mu bice bibiri bya gatatu no gupfusha abantu mu gice cya kabiri, ariko bikomeza gutuma abantu babarirwa mu bihumbi amagana bapfa kandi bikagira ibibazo by'ubuzima.
Kugabanya ubwandu bishobora guhitamo, ariko bikwiye gukomezwa igihe cyose virusi ikiri mu bantu (cyangwa kugeza igihe urukingo ruzaba rubonetse, niba ari rwo rwa mbere ruba rwaragaragaye), kuko iyo bitagenze bityo, ubwandu buzasubiraho vuba igihe ingamba zo kugabanya ubwandu zizaba zaragabanutse.
Ingamba z'igihe kirekire zo kurwanya icyorezo zagize ingaruka zikomeye ku mibereho y'abaturage no ku bukungu.
Nta muti wihariye wa virusi itera COVID-19 wemejwe, ariko hari ibikorwa byo kuwushyiraho biri gukorwa, birimo gupima imiti iriho.
Kunywa imiti yo kugabanya ibicurane, kunywa amazi ahagije no kuruhuka bishobora gutuma ibimenyetso bigabanuka.
Bisaba ko umuntu akenera imiti, umwuka, intravenous fluids n'ubufasha bwo guhumeka.
Kunywa ibiyobyabwenge bishobora gutuma umurwayi arushaho kuremba.
Hari imiti imwe n'imwe yari yarahawe uburenganzira bwo kuvura izindi ndwara za virusi iri gukorwaho ubushakashatsi kugira ngo ikoreshwe mu kuvura COVID-19.
OMS ivuga kandi ko "imiti imwe n'imwe yo mu rugo" ishobora kugabanya ibimenyetso byatewe na SARS-CoV-19.
OMS ivuga ko kongera ubushobozi no guhangana n'ibikenewe mu buzima bw'abarwayi ba COVID-19 ari intambwe y'ibanze mu gusubiza icyorezo.
ECDC n'ibiro by'umuryango w'abibumbye by'ubuzima (OMS) byo mu karere k'i Burayi byasohoye amabwiriza ku bitaro n'ibigo by'ubuzima bw'ibanze kugira ngo bikoreshe ibikoresho bitandukanye, harimo gushyira imbaraga mu bikorwa serivisi za laboratoire zo gupima COVID-19, niba bishoboka guhagarika ingendo zo guhitamo, gutandukanya no kwiherera abarwayi ba COVID-19, no kongera ubushobozi bwo kwita ku barwayi bafite ubwandu bw'icyorezo binyuze mu gutoza abakozi ndetse no kongera umubare w'abafite umwuka n'ibitanda.
Hari ibitekerezo byinshi ku birebana n'inkomoko y'ikibazo cya mbere (cyitwa "umurwayi w'ubusa").
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus cya mbere cyamenyekanye gishobora kugaragara ku itariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019 mu mujyi wa Wuhan, Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Mu gihe cy'ukwezi, umubare w'abanduye coronavirus muri Hubei wiyongereye buhoro buhoro.
Ibi bibazo byiganjemo ibijyanye n'isoko ry'ibiribwa byo mu nyanja rya Huanan, rigurisha n'inyamaswa nzima, kandi hari igitekerezo kivuga ko virusi ikomoka kuri imwe muri izi nyamaswa; cyangwa, mu yandi magambo, virusi ifite inkomoko zoonotic.
Ku itariki ya 30 Ukuboza, umugwi w'abaganga bo mu bitaro bya Wuhan Central Hospital wavuze ko "koronavirusi imeze nka SARS".
Abaganga umunani barimo Li Wenliang, bahawe igihano n'igipolisi cyo gukwirakwiza ibinyoma, naho undi, Ai Fen, ahanagurwa n'umuyobozi we kubera ko yatanze umuburo.
Komisiyo y'Ubuzima y'Umujyi wa Wuhan yahise itanga itangazo ku mugaragaro ku wa 31 Ukuboza, maze ibimenyesha OMS.
Hari abantu benshi bataramenyekana bagaragaye bafite indwara ya Pneumonia mu mujyi wa Wuhan, nyuma yaho batangira iperereza mu ntangiriro za Mutarama.
Mu ntangiriro no mu gicamunsi cya Mutarama 2020, virusi yageze mu zindi ntara zo mu Bushinwa, ifashwa n'ubwimukira mu gihe cy'umwaka mushya w'imleketi kandi kubera ko Wuhan ari ihuriro ry'ingendo n'ikigo cy'ingenzi cy'umurenge wa gari ya moshi.
Ku itariki ya 20 Mutarama, Ubushinwa bwavuze ko hashize umunsi umwe habonetse abantu bashya bagera ku 140, barimo abantu babiri i Beijing n'umwe i Shenzhen.
Amakuru akomeza agaragaza ko abantu 6,174 bamaze kugaragaza ibimenyetso ku wa 20 Mutarama 2020.Ku wa 26 Werurwe, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zarushijeho gukwirakwiza umubare munini w'abanduye mu Bushinwa no mu Butaliyani.Ku wa 9 Mata 2020, abantu basaga miliyoni 1.61 bamaze kuvugwa ku isi; abantu basaga 97,000 barapfuye, abandi basaga 364,000 bakize.
Ibihugu bigera kuri 200 n'uturere dutandukanye dufite nibura umuntu umwe ubarwayi.
Kubera icyorezo cy'indwara i Burayi, ibihugu byinshi byo mu karere ka Schengen byagabanyije ubwigenge bwo gutembera no gushyiraho amategeko agenga imipaka.
Igisubizo cy'igihugu kirimo ingamba zo kwirinda, urugero nko kwirinda icyorezo (cyitwa itegeko ryo kuguma mu rugo, itegeko ryo kurinda mu ngo, cyangwa itegeko ryo kwirinda mu karere) n'amasaha y'ijoro. Ku itariki ya 2 Mata, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 300, cyangwa hafi 90% by'abaturage, bari mu bwoko runaka bw'icyorezo cyo mu karere ka Quarantine muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, abantu barenga miliyoni 50 bari mu gace ka Quarantine muri Filipine, abantu bagera kuri miriyoni 59 bari mu gace ka Quarantine muri Afurika y'Epfo, n'abantu miliyari 1.3 bari mu gace ka Quarantine mu Buhinde.
Ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe, abantu miliyari 1.7 ku isi bari mu mimerere nk'iy'ubutagondwa, iki kizamuka kigera kuri miliyari 2.6 nyuma y'iminsi ibiri, ni ukuvuga nk'icya gatatu cy'abatuye isi.
Umuntu wa mbere wabonetse afite ubwandu bwa COVID-19 ashobora kugaruka ku itariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019 i Wuhan; raporo imwe itarakorwaho iperereza igaragaza ko abanduye ba mbere ari ku itariki ya 17 Ugushyingo.
Muganga Zhang Jixian yagenzuye icyorezo cy'indwara z'ubwonko zitagira impamvu ku itariki ya 26 Ukuboza; ibyo byibonekewe n'ibitaro bye byamenyesheje CDC Jianghan ku itariki ya 27 Ukuboza.
Igerageza ry'ubwoko bw'ibinyabuzima bwa mbere ku barwayi ku itariki ya 27 Ukuboza 2019 ryerekanye ko hari coronavirus isa na SARS.
Itangazo ryatanzwe n'Ikigo cy'Ubuzima cy'Umujyi wa Wuhan ku wa 31 Ukuboza.
WHO yahawe amakuru kuri uwo munsi.
Ubwo ubwo butumwa bwashyirwaga mu bikorwa, abaganga bo mu mujyi wa Wuhan baburiwe n'igipolisi ko "bakwirakwiza ibihuha" ku byerekeye iki cyorezo.
Komisiyo y'igihugu y'ubuzima ya Repubulika y'u Bushinwa mu mizo ya mbere yavuze ko nta "bihamya bifatika" byerekana ko umuntu ashobora kwandura indwara.
Mu mpera za Mutarama, leta y'u Bushinwa yatangije ubukangurambaga bw'inkomoko bw'ibihe byashize, nyuma y'aho akaba yarasobanuwe n'umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishyaka ry'abakomunisiti ry'u Bushinwa Xi Jinping nk' "intambara y'abaturage" yo guhagarika ikwirakwira ry'iyi virusi.
Mu gihe cy'imyiyerekano yitwa "imyiyerekano ikomeye cyane mu mateka y'abantu", ku itariki ya 23 Mutarama, hatangajwe ko hari gahunda yo guhagarika ingendo z'abantu bajya mu mujyi wa Wuhan no kuwusohokana, kandi ko yaguye mu mijyi 15 yo muri Hubei, igera ku bantu bagera kuri 57 miliyoni.
Gukoresha imodoka bwite birabujijwe mu mijyi.
Mu bihugu byinshi, kwizihiza Umwaka mushya w'Imyaka Mishahara (itariki ya 25 Mutarama) byarahagaritswe.
Abategetsi batangaje ko imirimo yo kubaka ibitaro by'agateganyo, Huoshenshan Hospital, izarangira mu minsi 10.
Hari n'ikindi bitaro byubatswe nyuma yaho, ari byo bitaro bya Leishenshan, kugira ngo bikire abandi barwayi.
Uretse ibitaro bishya byubatswe, Ubushinwa bwahinduye ibindi bigo 14 bya Wuhan, nk'ikigo cy'amakoraniro n'ikibuga cy'imikino, bikajya kuba ibitaro by'agateganyo. Ku wa 26 Mutarama, guverinoma yateguye izindi ngamba zo guhashya icyorezo cya COVID-19, harimo gutanga itangazo ry'ubuzima ku ba mukerarugendo no kwagura iminsi mikuru ya Festival y'Icyumweru.
Kaminuza zose n'amashuri yo mu gihugu hose na byo byafunzwe.
Intara ya Hong Kong na Macau zashyizeho ingamba zitandukanye, cyane cyane ku birebana n'amashuri n'amashuri makuru.
Mu bice bimwe na bimwe by'u Bushinwa hashyizweho ingamba zo gukora imirimo ya kure.
Ibihano by'ingendo byashyiriweho muri Hubei no hanze yayo.
Ibirori byo gutwara abantu n'ibintu byavuguruwe mu Bushinwa, ndetse n'inzu ndangamurage zo hirya no hino mu Bushinwa na zo zifunze by'agateganyo.
Ibirimo gukoreshwa mu gucunga ingendo z'abaturage mu mijyi myinshi, kandi bivugwa ko abantu bagera kuri miriyoni 760 (baba kimwe cya kabiri cy'abaturage) bahanganye n'ingamba zo kwirinda ingendo mu ngo.
Urugero, Beijing yashyizeho iminsi 14 y'ikiruhuko cy'abashyitsi mpuzamahanga bose binjira mu mujyi. Ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, icyorezo cyonyine cy'abashinwa bo ku butaka cyakwirakwijwe mu gihugu hagati mu minsi itanu mbere yaho, muri iki gihe cy'ingenzi zigarutse i Guangzhou ziva Istanbul.
Ku itariki ya 24 Werurwe 2020, Minisitiri w'Intebe w'u Bushinwa Li Keqiang yatangaje ko ubwandu bw'abanduye mu gihugu hagati bwafunzwe kandi ko icyorezo cyagenzurwa mu Bushinwa.
Ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe 2020, Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga ya Repubulika y'u Bushinwa yatangaje ko kwinjira ku bafite viza cyangwa uruhushya rwo gutura bizagororerwa guhera ku itariki ya 28 Werurwe, nta makuru asobanutse neza y'igihe iyi gahunda izarangirira.
Umuntu ushaka kwinjira mu Bushinwa agomba gusaba viza muri ambasade cyangwa muri konsulat.
Ku itariki ya 30 Werurwe, guverinoma y'u Bushinwa yashishikarije ubucuruzi n'inganda kongera gufungura no gutanga inguzanyo y'amafaranga ku bigo. Inama y'Igihugu yatangaje umunsi wo kwicuza itangira iminota itatu yo guceceka ku rwego rw'igihugu ku itariki ya 4 Mata saa kumi n'ebyiri, mu gihe cya Qingming Festival, nubwo guverinoma y'u Bushinwa yasabye imiryango gutanga icyubahiro ku rubuga rwa interineti mu gihe hari ibihano by'umubiri byakozwe kugira ngo birinde icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Ku itariki ya 20 Mutarama 2020, COVID-19 yemejwe ko yageze muri Koreya y'Epfo iturutse mu Bushinwa.
Ku itariki ya 20 Gashyantare, ikigo cy'igihugu gishinzwe ubuzima cyatangaje ko habayeho kwiyongera kw'abantu benshi bagaragaye ko banduye, ahanini bitewe n'ihuriro ry'imiryango mishya y'idini i Daegu, izwi nka Shincheonji Church of Jesus.
Abayoboke ba Shincheonji basuye Daegu baturutse mu mujyi wa Wuhan, bakekwaho kuba ari bo batangije iki cyorezo.
Ku itariki ya 22 Gashyantare, mu bigishwa ba Kiliziya 9,336, 1,261 cyangwa 13% by'abagize itorero, bavuze ko bafite ibimenyetso. Koreya y'Epfo yatangaje ko ifite igipimo cyo kuba maso cyo hejuru ku itariki ya 23 Gashyantare 2020.
Ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare, mu gihugu cya Koreya hemejwe ko hari abantu barenga 2.000 banduye, bakaba bariyongereye bagera ku 3.150 ku itariki ya 29 Gashyantare.
Ibigo byose bya gisirikare bya Koreya y'Epfo byashyizwe mu kato nyuma y'uko ibipimo byemeza ko abasirikare batatu banduye iyi virusi.
Ibi kandi byagize ingaruka ku ngendo z'indege kandi byahindutse. Koreya y'Epfo yashyizeho gahunda izwi ko ari yo nini kandi iteganijwe neza kurusha izindi ku isi yo gukaraba virusi mu baturage, gucibwa mu kato abantu bose banduye, no gukurikirana no gushyira mu kato abantu bahuye na bo.
Uburyo bwo gupima bwarimo inshingano zo gutanga amakuru y'ibimenyetso ku giti cyawe n'abantu bagarutse mu mahanga binyuze mu porogaramu za telefoni, gupima virusi ku buryo bworoshye cyangwa ku buryo bw'igitero ku munsi ukurikiyeho, no kongera ubushobozi bwo gupima abantu barenga 20,000 buri munsi.
Nubwo gahunda ya Koreya y'Epfo yagaragaje ko ifite icyo imaze kugabanya icyorezo cy'indwara, ntiyacyemeje ko abaturage bo muri Koreya y'Epfo bari mu kato.
Abaturage benshi b'igihugu cya Koreya bashyize umukono ku nyandiko zisaba ko Perezida Moon ashyirwa mu bikorwa kubera ko bavuga ko leta yakoze amakosa mu guhangana n'icyorezo, cyangwa se ko yashimye uko Perezida Moon yabyitwayemo.
Ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, Koreya y'Epfo yatangaje ko ifite umubare muto w'abanduye ku munsi umwe mu byumweru bine.
Ku itariki ya 29 Werurwe, havuzwe ko guhera ku itariki ya 1 Mata, abantu bose bavuye mu mahanga bazaba bari mu kato k'ibyumweru bibiri.
Nk'uko raporo z'itangazamakuru zo ku itariki ya 1 Mata zabitangaje, Koreya y'Epfo imaze kwakira ibisabwa n'ibihugu 121 byo gufasha mu gupima virusi.
Iran yatangaje ko ku itariki ya 19 Gashyantare i Qom, abantu babiri bapfuye, nk'uko bivugwa n'ubushikiranganji bw'ubuzima n'uburezi mu buvuzi.
Mu ngamba za mbere leta yatangaje harimo guhagarika ibitaramo n'ibindi bikorwa by'umuco, imikino, n'amasengesho yo ku wa Gatanu, ndetse no gufunga kaminuza, ibigo by'uburezi bwo mu rwego rwo hejuru n'amashuri.
Iran yashyize hanze miliyari eshanu z'amadolari y'u Rwanda kugira ngo irwanye iyi virusi.
Perezida Hassan Rouhani yavuze ku wa 26 Gashyantare 2020 ko nta gahunda yo gushyira mu kato akarere gashyizweho n'icyorezo, ko abantu bonyine bazajya mu kato.
Mu kwezi kwa gatatu, hatangajwe gahunda yo kugabanya ingendo z'abantu benshi, nubwo ingendo nyinshi z'abantu benshi zagiye zigenda zigerageza kugera mu mwaka mushya wa Peresi.
Ikibanza cy'ugusengeramo cy'aba Shia i Qom kizakomeza gufungurirwa abapadiri kugeza ku itariki ya 16 Werurwe 2020.
Mu gihe hari ikirego cy'uko umubare w'ibiza muri Irani wagabanutse, ibihugu birenga icumi byasubiye inyuma ku byago byabyo muri Irani ku wa 28 Gashyantare, ibyo bikaba bigaragaza ko umubare w'ibiza ushobora kuba mubi cyane ugereranyije n'ibyabaye ku bantu 388 Leta ya Irani yatangaje kuri uwo munsi.
Inteko Ishinga Amategeko ya Irani yafunze, ku itariki ya 3 Werurwe, 23 mu 290 bayigize bagaragaye ko banduye iyi virusi.
Ku itariki ya 12 Werurwe, Human Rights Watch yasabye abayobozi ba gereza za Irani kurekura burundu abarwanashyaka bazira imyigaragambyo y'amahoro, kandi, mu gihe gito, barekura imfungwa zose zifite uburenganzira.
Byagaragajwe ko hari ibyago byinshi byo gukwirakwira mu bigo bifunze nka za gereza, na byo bikaba bitagira ubuvuzi buhagije.
Ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe, guverinoma ya Irani yatangaje ko abantu 100 bapfuye mu munsi umwe, ari bo bantu benshi cyane muri icyo gihugu kuva icyorezo cyatangira.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 17 Werurwe, nibura abanyapolitiki 12 cyangwa abayobozi ba Irani bariho cyangwa bariho ubu, barapfuye bazize iyo ndwara.
Ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, Irani yahuye n'abantu bashya 50 bagerwaho na coronavirus buri saha n'umuntu umwe upfa buri minota icumi.
Hari umukozi wa OMS wavuze ko mu gihugu cya Iran hari abantu benshi cyane, bashobora kuba ari inshuro eshanu z'ababa baramaze kwandura.
Byongeye kandi, byavuzwe ko ibihano bya Amerika kuri Irani bishobora kugira ingaruka ku bushobozi bw'igihugu bwo guhangana n'icyorezo cya virusi.
Umukuru w'Umuryango w'Abibumbye wita ku burenganzira bw'ikiremwamuntu yasabye ko ibihano by'ubukungu byoroha ku bihugu byugarijwe n'icyorezo, harimo na Iran.
Ku wa 31 Mutarama, icyorezo cyemejwe ko cyakwirakwiriye mu Butaliyani ubwo abashyitsi babiri b'Abashinwa bageragezaga kwandura SARS-CoV-2 i Roma.
Ibi byago byatangiye kwiyongera cyane bituma leta y'u Butaliyani ihagarika ingendo zose ziva mu Bushinwa no mu Bushinwa, ndetse itangaza ko hari imimerere y'ubutagondwa.
Nyuma, icyunamo cy'abanduye COVID-19 badafite aho bahuriye nacyo cyagaragaye, gitangira n'abanduye 16 bemejwe mu ntara ya Lombardy ku wa 21 Gashyantare.Ku wa 22 Gashyantare, Inama y'Abaminisitiri yatangaje itegeko rishya ryo guhagarika icyorezo, rivuga ko rigomba guhagarika abantu barenga 50,000 bo mu migi 11 itandukanye yo mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani.
Minisitiri w'Intebe Giuseppe Conte yagize ati "Mu karere k'icyorezo, abantu ntibemerewe kujya hanze.
Ku itariki ya 4 Werurwe, leta y'u Butaliyani yategetse ko amashuri yose na za kaminuza bifungwa burundu mu gihugu cyose, ubwo abaturage b'u Butaliyani bageraga ku bantu 100.
Imikino yose ikomeye, harimo imikino ya shampiyona ya Serie A, izaba yafunze kugeza muri Mata, ariko ku itariki ya 9 Werurwe, imikino yose izaba yahagaritswe burundu nibura ukwezi kumwe.
Ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Conte yategetse ko ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi hafi ya byose bihagarikwa, uretse ibigo by'ubucuruzi n'ubuvuzi. Ku itariki ya 6 Werurwe, Ishuri rikuru ry'Ubutaliyani ry'Ubuzima, Ububabare, Ubuzima n'Icyorezo (SIAARTI) ryasohoye inama ku bijyanye n'amahame y'ubuvuzi ku birebana n'imikorere y'imiti ishobora gukoreshwa.
Ku itariki ya 19 Werurwe, u Butaliyani bwafashe umwanya wa Ubushinwa nk'igihugu gifite umubare munini w'abantu bapfa bazize coronavirus ku isi nyuma yo gutanga amakuru y'abantu 3,405 bapfuye bazize icyorezo.
Ku itariki ya 22 Werurwe, u Burusiya bwagiye butumiza indege z'intambara icyenda zitwara ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Butaliyani.
Ku itariki ya 5 Mata, mu Butaliyani hari abantu 128.948 banduye, 15.887 bapfuye, n'abantu 21.815 bakize, abenshi muri bo bakaba bari mu karere ka Lombardy.
Hari raporo ya CNN yavuze ko ikintu cyatumye umubare w'abapfa wiyongera ari uko abaturage benshi bo mu Butaliyani bageze mu za bukuru batagira ubushobozi bwo gupima abantu bose banduye iyi virusi.
Mu mizo ya mbere, icyo gihugu cyitabiriye iyi virusi mu buryo bwihuse cyane mu bihugu byayibasiwe, kandi kugeza ku itariki ya 18 Werurwe 2020, guverinoma y'u Bwongereza ntiyafashe ingamba zo kugabanya imikorere y'abaturage cyangwa gushyira mu kato abaturage bayo.
Ku wa 16 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Boris Johnson yatangaje ko agomba guhagarika ingendo zose n'imishyikirano idakenewe n'abantu, kandi agasaba abantu gukora imirimo yo mu rugo, niba bishoboka, ndetse bakirinda ahantu nk'aho baba, amabariro, amazu y'imikino.
Ku itariki ya 20 Werurwe, guverinoma yatangaje ko ahantu h'uburuhukiro hose, urugero nk'aho babaga n'amazu yo gukiniramo, hagomba gufungwa vuba uko bishoboka kose, kandi isezeranya ko izatanga amafaranga agera kuri 80% y'imishahara y'abakozi, agera ku kigero cya £2,500 buri kwezi, kugira ngo birinde ubushomeri mu bihe by'akaga. Ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe yatangaje ingamba zikomeye zo kugabanya abantu benshi guhurira hamwe, no kugabanya ingendo no gukora imirimo yo hanze gusa ku bikorwa by'ingenzi cyane.
Mu buryo bunyuranye n'uko byari bimeze mu ngamba zabanje, iyi migambi yashyizweho n'igipolisi binyuze mu gutanga amande no gusenya amakipe.
Ubucuruzi bwinshi bwasabwe gufunga, uretse ubucuruzi bwasabwe ko ari "ingenzi", bukora muri supermarchés, pharmacies, banki, ibigo by'ubucuruzi, pompe z'ibikomoka kuri peteroli n'ibigo by'ubucuruzi.
Ku wa 20 Mutarama, icyorezo cya COVID-19 cya mbere cyemejwe cyagaragaye muri leta ya Washington mu majyaruguru ashyira uburengerazuba, mu mugabo wasubiye mu gihugu cye avuye i Wuhan ku wa 15 Mutarama.
Ku itariki ya 29 Mutarama, hashyizweho itsinda ry'abafasha kurwanya Coronavirus muri White House.
Ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama, ubutegetsi bwa Trump bwatangaje ko hari imimerere y'ubuzima rusange kandi bwahaye abantu bari baturutse mu Bushinwa ivangura ry'ingendo.
Ku itariki ya 28 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya indwara, ari cyo kigo kizwi cyane mu by'ubuzima rusange muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, cyatangaje ko cyatangiye gukora ibikoresho byo gupima.
Nyamara, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zatinze gutangiza ibizamini bituma abantu batamenya neza umubare nyawo w'icyorezo icyo gihe.
Gusuzuma byasenywe n'ibikoresho by'impuha byakozwe na leta muri Gashyantare, kubura kwemererwa na leta ku bikoresho bitari ibya leta (bihawe n'abanyeshuri, ibigo by'amashuri n'ibitaro) kugeza mu mpera za Gashyantare, n'ibisabwa by'ubudahangarwa ku bantu bifuzaga gupimwa kugeza mu ntangiriro za Werurwe (ku bw'ibyo, bisaba ko abaganga babaha amabwiriza).
Kugeza ku itariki ya 27 Gashyantare, ikinyamakuru The Washington Post cyavuze ko nta bigeragezo 4.000 byakozwe muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 13 Werurwe, The Atlantic yatangaje ko nta bigeragezo 14,000 byakozwe.
Ku itariki ya 22 Werurwe, Associated Press yongeyeho iti "abantu benshi bafite ibimenyetso n'amabwiriza y'abaganga bategereje amasaha n'iminsi kugira ngo bagerweho ibizamini".
Amashuri yo mu karere ka Seattle yahagaritse amasomo ku ya 3 Werurwe, ndetse mu gice cya Werurwe, amashuri yo hirya no hino mu gihugu yarafunze. Ku ya 6 Werurwe 2020, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zabwiwe ko ibipimo by'ingaruka za coronavirus nshya ku gihugu byatewe n'itsinda ry'abahanga mu by'indwara zo mu rwego rw'ubwonko bo muri Imperial College London.
Kuri uwo munsi, Perezida Trump yashyize umukono ku itegeko ry'ibikoresho by'inyongera by'itegurwa ry'icyorezo cya Coronavirus, ryatanze imari ya $8.3 miliyari ku rwego rw'ubukungu bw'icyorezo ku nzego za leta kugira ngo zitabire iki cyorezo.
Iyo kompanyi yashyizeho amategeko agenga ingendo z'abakozi, igahagarika inama, kandi igashishikariza abakozi gukora imirimo yo mu rugo.
Ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe, Trump yatangaje ko hari iminsi 30 yo guhagarika ingendo mu bihugu byinshi by'i Burayi uretse mu Bwongereza, izarangira ku itariki ya 13 Werurwe.
Bukeye bwaho, yaguyeho ibyo bihano kugira ngo ashyireho u Bwongereza na Irilande.
Ku itariki ya 13 Werurwe, yatangaje imimerere y'amajyambere y'igihugu kugira ngo hatangwe amafaranga y'ishami yo guhangana n'ikibazo cy'amacakubiri.
Guhera ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe, ubucuruzi bwinshi bwafunze cyangwa bukagabanya amasaha yo gukora muri Amerika yose mu rwego rwo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'iyi virusi.
Ku itariki ya 17 Werurwe, icyorezo cyemejwe mu bihugu 50 no mu Karere ka Columbia. Ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, New York City yatangaje ko ifite abantu 10.700 banduye coronavirus, ni ukuvuga ko ari benshi cyane ugereranyije n'abanduye bose muri Koreya y'Epfo.
Ku itariki ya 25 Werurwe, guverineri wa New York yavuze ko ibyo bihano bisa n'aho byatanze umusaruro kuko umubare w'abanduye wiyongereyeho kabiri, wavuye ku minsi 2.0 ugera ku minsi 4.7.
Ku itariki ya 28 Werurwe, hari abantu 32.308 banduye muri New York City, abandi 672 bahitanwa na coronavirus. Ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zavuze ko zifite abantu benshi banduye coronavirus kurusha ikindi gihugu cyose ku isi, harimo Ubushinwa n'u Butaliyani. Ku itariki ya 8 Mata, hari abantu 400,335 banduye muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, abandi 12,841 bapfuye.
Nkuko byatangajwe n'itangazamakuru ku wa 30 Werurwe, Perezida wa Amerika Trump yafashe icyemezo cyo kongera amabwiriza yo kugabanya imikorere y'abaturage kugeza ku wa 30 Mata.
Uwo munsi, ubwato bw'ibitaro bwa USNS Comfort bwari bufite ibitanda bigera ku 1.000, bwarohamye i New York.
Ku itariki ya 3 Mata, Amerika yari imaze guhitana abantu 884 bahitanywe na coronavirus mu masaha 24.
Mu ntara ya New York, abantu barenga 100,000 bamaze kwandura kuri uyu wa 3 Mata, ibiro by'ishami by'Amerika by'Amerika byashyizweho impaka ku byo byamagana ko byibura ko byibanda ku butumwa bw'ubutegetsi bw'ubuzima n'abahanga mu by'ikoranabuhanga, byo gushyira hamwe itangazo rya leta n'ibitabo by'ikoranabuhanga ku biro bya Visi Perezida Mike Pence.
Muri rusange, imyemerere y'ubutegetsi bwa Trump mu bibazo by'ingorane yagabanyijemo ibice mu rwego rw'abafatanyabikorwa.
Bamwe mu bayobozi ba Amerika n'abanyamakuru banenze ko Amerika ishingiye ku kwinjiza ibintu by'ingenzi mu Bushinwa, harimo n'ibikoresho by'ingenzi by'ubuvuzi.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku ngengabitekerezo z'ingendo z'indege bwakoreshejwe mu gusesengura no guhanura ingengabitekerezo z'ubwirakabiri bw'ingendo, bwasohotse mu kinyamakuru cyitwa The Journal of Travel Medicine mu kwezi kwa Mutarama 2020.
Nk'uko bigaragara mu 2018 n'umuryango mpuzamahanga wita ku ikoranabuhanga mu gutwara abantu n'ibintu, abantu benshi bavuye mu mujyi wa Wuhan ni bo bari i Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo na Taipei.
Dubai, Sydney na Melbourne na byo bivugwa ko ari ahantu henshi abantu bajya baturutse i Wuhan.
Bali bivugwa ko ari yo itagira ubushobozi bwo kwitegura mu mijyi 20 ikundwa cyane, mu gihe mijyi yo muri Australia ari yo itagira ubushobozi bwo kwitegura.
Bivugwa ko hakiri byinshi bitaramenyekana kuri COVID-19, kandi ko Australia izashyira imbaraga mu gucunga imipaka no mu itumanaho mu guhangana n'icyorezo.
Ku itariki ya 21 Werurwe, Ositaraliya yatangaje ko hari imimerere y'ubudahangarwa.
Kubera ko hari ingendo z'abantu benshi mu mujyi wa Wuhan n'uwa Hubei, ibihugu bimwe na bimwe biteganya gutahuka abaturage n'abakozi ba bya diplomate muri ako gace, cyane cyane ku ndege z'ubwishyu ziva mu bihugu by'iwabo, bifashijwemo n'ubuyobozi bw'u Bushinwa.
Kanada, Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, Ubuyapani, Ubuhinde, Sri Lanka, Ositaraliya, Ufaransa, Arjantine, U Budage na Tayilande ni bimwe mu bihugu bya mbere bigamije guhunga abaturage babyo.
Pakistan yavuze ko itazatura abaturage bayo mu Bushinwa.
Ku itariki ya 7 Gashyantare, Brezili yavanye muri icyo gihugu abantu 34 b'Abanyabrezili cyangwa abagize imiryango y'Abanyabrezili, hamwe n'Abanyapolonye bane, Umushinwa umwe n'Umuhindi umwe.
Abaturage bo muri Polonye, Ubushinwa n'u Buhindi bahawe ubwato bwo mu Burusiya, aho indege y'icyo gihugu yahagaze mbere yo kujya muri Burezili.
Abaturage bo muri Brezili bagiye i Wuhan bashyizwe mu kato ku kigo cya gisirikare kiri hafi ya Brasília.
Kuri uwo munsi, Abakanada 215 (176 bo mu ndege ya mbere na 39 bo mu ndege ya kabiri yahawe na leta ya Amerika) bahungiye mu kigo cy'indege cya CFB Trenton, mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare, indi ndege yari itwaye Abanyakanada 185 yari ivuye i Wuhan, yageze ku kibuga cy'indege cya CFB Trenton.
Abayobozi ba Australia bavuye muri icyo gihugu ku itariki ya 3 na 4 Gashyantare, maze bahamagara abaturage babo 277 muri gereza ya Christmas Island, yahinduwe icyumba cy'ubwirinzi, aho bari kumara iminsi 14.
Indege yo kuvana muri Nouvelle-Zélande yageze i Auckland ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare; abari bayirimo (bari bamwe baturutse muri Australia no muri Pasifika) bari mu kato ku kigo cya gisirikare cya gisirikare cy'i Whangaparoa, mu majyaruguru ya Auckland.
Ku itariki ya 15 Gashyantare, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zatangaje ko zari guhunga Abanyamerika bari ku bwato bwa Diamond Princess.
Ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare, indege yari itwaye abagenzi 129 bo muri Kanada bari bamaze kuvanwa muri Diamond Princess, yageze i Trenton, muri Ontario.
Mu ntangiriro z'ukwezi kwa gatatu, Leta y'u Buhinde yatangiye guhunga abaturage bayo bava muri Irani. Ku itariki ya 14 Werurwe, indege ya South African Airways yari yarashyizweho na Leta ya Afurika y'Epfo yashubije abaturage bayo 112.
Gusuzuma kwa muganga kwabaye mbere yo kugenda, maze abantu bane bo muri Afurika y'Epfo bagaragaje ibimenyetso bya coronavirus basiga inyuma kugira ngo bagabanye ibyago.
Abanyarwanda b'Afurika y'Epfo bonyine ni bo bahabwa uburenganzira bwo gusubira mu bihugu byabo.
Binyuze ku bipimo byafashwe, abantu bose bo muri Afurika y'Epfo bahawe uburenganzira bwo gukora imirimo, harimo abasirikare, abagenzi, abakozi bo mu mahoteli, abapolisi n'abasirikare bakoraga ibikorwa by'ubutabazi; bose bakomeje gushyirwa mu kato mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 bari muri The Ranch Resort.
Ku itariki ya 20 Werurwe, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zatangiye gukura ingabo zayo muri Irak kubera icyorezo.
Ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare, Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga y'u Bushinwa yatangaje ko ibihugu 21 (birimo Belarus, Pakistan, Trinidad na Tobago, Misiri, na Irani) byohereje ubufasha mu Bushinwa.
Abanyeshuri b'Abashinwa bo muri za kaminuza zitandukanye zo muri Amerika bifatanyije kohereza imfashanyo mu bice by'u Bushinwa byugarijwe n'iyi virusi, hamwe n'itsinda ry'abantu bifatanyije baturutse mu gace ka Chicago; bavuga ko bageze ku bihumbi 50 by'amasikoni ya N95 ku bitaro byo mu ntara ya Hubei ku wa 30 Mutarama.
Ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare, Bill na Melinda Gates batangaje ko bahawe miliyoni 100 z'amadolari OMS kugira ngo ikomeze ubushakashatsi ku nkingo n'imihati yo kuzirwanya, kandi ikomeze kurinda "abaturage bari mu kaga muri Afurika no muri Aziya y'Epfo".
Interaksyon yatangaje ko leta y'Ubushinwa yatanze amasiki 200.000 kuri Filipine ku wa 6 Gashyantare, nyuma y'uko Senateri Richard Gordon yohereje amasiki miliyoni 3.16 i Wuhan.
Ku itariki ya 19 Gashyantare, Umuryango Mpuzamahanga w'Abasangwabutaka wo muri Singapuru (Singapore Red Cross) watangaje ko ugiye kohereza inkunga ya miriyoni 2.26 z'amadolari y'Amerika ku Bushinwa.
U Buyapani bwatanze agapfukamunwa k'uruhu miliyoni imwe ku mugabane wa Wuhan, u Turukiya bwatanze ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, u Burusiya bwatanze toni zisaga 13 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi i Wuhan, Malaysia itangaza ko yatanze miliyoni 18 z'amafaranga y'amaboko y'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa, u Budage bwatanze toni zisaga 10.000 z'imyenda ya Hazmat, Amerika yohereje toni 17.8 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa ndetse isezeranya ko izongeraho miliyoni 100 z'amadolari mu buryo bw'ubufasha mu rwego rw'amafaranga ku bihugu byibasiwe n'iki cyorezo.
Mu kwezi kwa gatatu, Ubushinwa, Cuba n'Uburusiya byohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'abahanga mu gufasha u Butaliyani guhangana n'icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Umushoramari Jack Ma yohereje ibikoresho byo gupima miliyoni 1.1 n'amasiki y'uruhu miliyoni 6 n'imyenda 60,000 yo kwirinda mu mujyi wa Addis Abeba muri Etiyopiya, kugira ngo bizabone gutangwa n'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'Afurika.
Hanyuma yohereje ibikoresho 5.000 byo gupima, udupfukamunwa 100.000 n'imashini 5 z'ubuhumekero muri Panama.
Ma yatanze n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi muri Canada.
Urugero, u Butaliyani bwasabye ko hakorwa ibikoresho 58,000 by'ubushakashatsi ku bwoko bwa coronavirus byakozwe n'Ubushinwa, bifite igipimo cyo kwihutisha ku kigero cya 30% gusa; mu gihe u Buholandi bwasabye ko hagira amasiki 600,000 y'uruhu rw'Ubushinwa.
U Bubiligi na bwo bwafashe udupfukamunwa 100,000 tudashobora gukoresha, twibaza ko twavuye mu Bushinwa, ariko mu by'ukuri tukava muri Kolombiya.
Ku rundi ruhande, ubufasha bw'u Bushinwa bwarakiriwe neza mu bice bimwe na bimwe bya Amerika y'Epfo na Afurika. Ku itariki ya 2 Mata, Banki y'Isi yatangije igikorwa cyo gufasha ibihugu biri mu nzira y'amajyambere mu buryo bw'impanuka.
OMS yashimiye cyane ingamba za leta y'u Bushinwa mu gucunga no gukumira iki cyorezo.
OMS yabonye itandukaniro hagati y'icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2002-2004 ubwo abategetsi b'u Bushinwa bashinjwaga ko bahishaga abantu bigatuma batagira icyo bakora ku buryo ubu ubukangurambaga n'ibibazo byugarije muri iki gihe, aho leta nkuru "itanga ibisobanuro buri gihe kugira ngo birinde imvururu z'iminsi mikuru y'umwaka mushya".
Ku itariki ya 23 Mutarama, mu rwego rwo gusubiza ku cyemezo cya leta y'u Burayi cyo gushyiraho itegeko ribuza ingendo mu mujyi wa Wuhan, uhagarariye OMS Gauden Galea yavuze ko nubwo iyo ngingo "biragaragara ko atari inama ya OMS", ariko ko ari "ikimenyetso gikomeye cyane cy'icyifuzo cyo guhagarika icyorezo aho icyorezo cyagaragaye cyane" kandi ko "kitigeze kibaho mu mateka y'ubuzima bw'abaturage".Ku itariki ya 30 Mutarama, nyuma yo kwemeza ko abantu banduye mu bantu hanze y'u Bushinwa no kongera umubare w'abanduye mu bindi bihugu, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari kimwe mu byerekeranye n'ubuzima bw'abaturage buhangayikishije Isi (PHEIC), ari nacyo cya gatandatu cya PHEIC cyakozwe kuva mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya za filimi z'ingurube mu mwaka wa 2009.
Umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS Tedros Adhanom yavuze ko PHEIC yashyizwe ahagaragara kubera ko "hari ibyago byo gukwirakwira ku isi hose, cyane cyane mu bihugu bifite amikoro make n'ibihugu bigezweho bitarigeze bifite gahunda z'ubuzima zifite ubushobozi.
Tedros yashubije ku birebana no gushyiraho ibihano ku ngendo, avuga ko "nta mpamvu yo gushyiraho ingamba zitangiza ingendo n'ubucuruzi mpuzamahanga bidakenewe" kandi ko "OMS idashyigikira ibihano ku bucuruzi n'imihanda".
Ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare, OMS yasabye umuryango w'isi yose gutanga inkunga y'amadolari agera kuri miriyoni 675 y'amadolari azakoreshwa mu gushyigikira gahunda yo kwitegura ibihugu bifite amikoro make, ivuga ko ari ngombwa gushyigikira ibihugu "bitagira uburyo bwo gutahura abantu banduye iyo icyorezo kiza gukwirakwira".
Tedros yakomeje avuga ko "imbaraga zacu ziri ku isonga ry'ibyago" kandi asaba umuryango mpuzamahanga "guhora uhinga uyu munsi cyangwa ugishyura ibiciro byinshi nyuma".Mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru cyo ku wa 11 Gashyantare, OMS yashyizeho COVID-19 nk'izina ry'indwara y'iyi virusi.
Kuri uwo munsi, Tedros yavuze ko Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Umuryango w'Abibumbye, António Guterres, yemeye gutanga "igisubizo cy'uko ubutegetsi bw'Umuryango w'Abibumbye bufite imbaraga zose".
Nyuma yaho, Umuryango w'Abibumbye watangije Itsinda ry'Ubutegetsi bw'Ibihe kugira ngo rijye rihuza ibikorwa byose by'Umuryango w'Abibumbye, WHO ivuga ko bizatuma "bashobora kwibanda ku buzima, mu gihe ibindi bigo bishobora gukoresha ubuhanga bwabyo mu guhangana n'ingaruka z'icyorezo mu mibereho rusange, mu bukungu no mu iterambere".
Ku itariki ya 14 Gashyantare, hashyizweho itsinda ry'imirimo yifatanyije n'u Bushinwa riyobowe na OMS; rigamije guha ingufu inzobere mpuzamahanga na OMS mu Bushinwa mu rwego rwo gufasha mu miyoborere yo mu gihugu ndetse no gusuzuma "ibipimo by'icyorezo n'icyorezo cy'indwara" binyuze mu gukora ibiganiro n'inama n'inzego z'icyiciro cy'igihugu bireba no gusura mu kibuga kugira ngo barebe "ingaruka ibikorwa byo kurwanya ku rwego rw'intara n'uturere, birimo no gushyiraho gahunda z'imikorere y'umujyi n'iy'icyaro". Ku itariki ya 25 Gashyantare, OMS yatangaje ko "isi igomba gukora byinshi kurushaho kugira ngo yitegure icyorezo cya Coronavirus" kandi ko nubwo hakiri kare cyane ko cyitwa icyorezo, ibihugu bigomba kuba "bicyiteguye".
Mu gusubiza icyorezo cyabaye muri Iran, OMS yohereje itsinda ry'umurimo w'ubumwe muri icyo gihugu kugira ngo rigenzure uko ibintu byifashe. Ku wa 28 Gashyantare, abayobozi ba OMS bavuze ko ibipimo by'iterabwoba rya coronavirus ku rwego rw'isi bizakuzwa kuva "kirenga" kugera "ikirenga cyane", ibi bikaba ari ibipimo byo kwirinda no gupima ibyago byinshi.
Mu itangazo, Mike Ryan, umuyobozi mukuru w'ikigo cy'umuryango w'abibumbye cyita ku buzima, yatanze umuburo agira ati "iki ni cyo gihe cya buri butegetsi bwose ku isi bwo guhangana n'ukuri: nimukanguke.
Iyi virusi ishobora kuza aho uri kandi ugomba kuba witeguye, " kandi ugasaba ko ingamba zo kurwanya zishobora gufasha isi kwirinda" ikibi cyane. "
Ryan yakomeje avuga ko amakuru y'ubu adashobora gutuma abayobozi b'ubuzima bwa rusange bavuga ko hari icyorezo ku isi hose, ndetse avuga ko gutangaza ko ari icyorezo byumvikanisha ko "mu by'ukuri twemera ko abantu bose ku isi bazaba baranduye iyi virusi".
Ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe, OMS yatangaje ko icyorezo cya Coronavirus ari icyorezo.
Umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS yavuze ko OMS "ishishikajwe cyane n'umubare w'icyorezo n'ubukana bwacyo, ndetse n'umubare w'abantu batagira icyo bakora". OMS yahawe ibisobanuro bikomeye kubera ko itagishoboye guhangana n'icyorezo, harimo gutinda gutangaza imyivumbagatanyo y'ubuzima rusange no gushyira virusi mu cyorezo.
Imwe mu myifatire mibi yagize harimo petition yashyizweho umukono n'abantu 733,000 ku itariki ya 6 Mata, yandikiwe Umuyobozi Mukuru wa OMS Tedros Adhanom asaba ko yegura.
Ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe 2020, inzobere z'umuryango w'abibumbye z'uburenganzira bw'ikiremwamuntu z'uburyo bwinshi zemeje ko uburenganzira bw'umuntu wese buhabwa agaciro mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Uwo mutwe w'impuguke wavuze ko buri wese afite uburenganzira bwo gutanga ingamba zo kurokora ubuzima, kandi ko leta ari yo izabigenza ityo.
Iri tsinda ryashimangiye ko kubura umutungo cyangwa ubwishingizi bw'ubuzima bidakwiye gukoreshwa nk'impongano yo guhaririza ubwoko runaka.
Abahanga bashimangira ko buri wese afite uburenganzira ku buzima, harimo abafite ubumuga, abantu batagira aho babogamira, abageze mu za bukuru, impunzi, abakene cyane, abari muri gereza, impunzi n'abandi bakeneye inkunga ya leta.
Amashyirahamwe ya leta mpuzamahanga arimo agerageza guhangana n'ingaruka za sosiyete n'ubukungu by'ikibazo cya COVID-19.
