Bamwe mu batanga ibitekerezo bavuga ko iyo ngingo yagamije kurinda umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishyaka ry'abakomunisiti ry'u Bushinwa Xi Jinping uburakari bw'abaturage ku cyorezo cya coronavirus.
Bamwe mu bayobozi b'u Bushinwa, nka Zhao Lijian, banze kwemera ko icyorezo cya coronavirus cyatangiye i Wuhan, kandi bashyigikira igitekerezo cy'umugambi w'ivugurura ku COVID-19 ko ari icy'Amerika cyangwa icy'u Butaliyani.
