Gutegeka akaga k'akazi ka COVID-19 ni ugushyira mu bikorwa uburyo bwo kwirinda impanuka zo mu kazi no kwirinda indwara ya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Gutegeka akaga gakwiye mu kazi gashingiye ku mwanya w'akazi n'akazi ukora, hashingiwe ku rwego rw'ibyago by'ibanze, ku rwego rw'uburwayi mu baturage, no ku bintu by'ibyago by'umukozi umwe n'umwe ushobora kwandura COVID-19.
