Muri abo bantu harimo abakozi bagirana ubucuti n'abantu benshi, urugero nk'amashuri, ahantu ho gukorera abantu benshi, n'ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi.
Kugabanya akaga k'iyi kipe, uretse kwirinda indwara z'ibanze, harimo guhumeka hakoreshejwe ibigega by'umwuka bifite ubushobozi buhagije, kwirinda kurira, no gutanga ubwirinzi mu gihe uhuye n'abarwayi ba COVID-19.
OSHA ivuga ko abakozi b'ubuzima n'abapfuye bagaragarijwe abantu bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho kuba bafite COVID-19 bafite ibyago byinshi byo gushyirwa mu ndwara, bikaba byongera ibyago byo gushyirwa mu ndwara nyinshi cyane iyo abakozi bakoze ingeso zo gukora aerosol kuri, cyangwa gufata cyangwa gufata ibipimo by'abantu bazi cyangwa bakekwaho kuba bafite COVID-19.
