b'Ingirabuzima fatizo (ACE2) ni ingirabuzima fatizo ifata ubwirinzi ku gice cyo hanze cy'ingirabuzima fatizo (imumbera) mu mahaha, mu mitsi, mu mutima, mu mpyiko no mu mara.
ACE2 ifite ibikorwa bitandukanye n'ingingo z'ingenzi z'ingenzi zigize ingirabuzima fatizo (ACE), igabanya ingirabuzima fatizo (angiotensin-II) kandi igahaza ingirabuzima fatizo (angiotensin-1-7), bigatuma iba umuti ugaragaza icyizere cyo kuvura indwara z'umutima.
Abantu bakunze kwita ACE2 hACE2.
Ingirabuzima fatizo y'umurava (angiotensin 2) ni ingirabuzima fatizo irimo zinc iri ku rwego rw'ingirabuzima fatizo z'ingirabuzima fatizo (endothelial) n'izindi ngirabuzima fatizo.
Poroteyine ACE2 ifite domain M2 ya peptidase terminal-N n'ingingo y'icyitwa amini acids collectrin terminal-C.
ACE2 ni umutingito w'ingirabuzimafatizo imwe y'indwara y'ibinyabuzima, ifite ingingo zikora ku buryo bw'enzimati zigaragara ku gice cy'ingirabuzimafatizo cyo mu mahaha no mu zindi ngirabuzimafatizo.
Ingingo ya ACE2 yo mu cyuma cy'ubutayu, itandukanywa n'indi ngingo y'umubiri, yitwa sheddase, maze igatanga ingirabuzima fatizo mu maraso, amaherezo igasohoka mu munyu.
ACE2 iboneka mu bice byinshi by'umubiri: ACE2 iboneka mu bice byinshi by'umubiri, cyane cyane mu bice byinshi by'umubiri, cyane cyane mu bice byinshi by'umubiri, mu bice byinshi by'umubiri.
Igikorwa cyo gutangiza imikorere ya ACE2 nacyo kiboneka mu bice by'ibere, mu gice cy'ibere, mu gice cy'ibere, mu gice cy'ibere.
Icy'ingenzi mu kazi ka ACE2 ni uko iba igamije gushyira mu gaciro.
ACE ihindura ingirabuzima fatizo ya angiotensin I mu ingirabuzima fatizo ya angiotensin II.
Amaherezo, ACE2 igabanya amino acid ya phenylalanine ihitana na carboxylate ku gice cy'umubiri cy'umubiri cy'umubiri cy'umubiri cyitwa angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) ikayihindura angiotensin (1-7) ihindura amaraso (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 ishobora no gusenya izindi peptide nyinshi zirimo [des-Arg9] -bradikinine, apelin, neurotensin, dinorphine A, na ghrelin.
ACE2 kandi igenzura ingendo z'ibinyabuzima by'umwimerere bya SLC6A19 na SLC6A19 kandi ifitanye isano n'indwara ya Hartnup.
Nk'imiterere y'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima, ACE2 ikora nk'aho ari cyo cyinjira cy'ingenzi mu ngirabuzimafatizo za koronavirusi zitandukanye, zirimo HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virusi iteza SARS); na SARS-CoV-2 (virusi iteza COVID-19).
By'umwihariko, guhuza poroteyine ya S1 ku muvuduko cyangwa igitereko cya SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV2 n'urwego rwa ACE2 ku gice cy'ingirabuzimafatizo ku gice cy'ingirabuzimafatizo bigatuma virusi n'ingirabuzimafatizo bihinduka indusobe mu gice cy'ingirabuzimafatizo.
Iyi gahunda yo kwinjira muri virusi ikeneye kandi ko poroteyine ya S igomba gutangwa na serine protease ya TMPRSS2, ubu ikaba irimo gukorwaho ubushakashatsi ku buhagarike bwayo nk'umuti ushobora kuvura.
Icyakora, hari inzego nyinshi z'ubucuruzi n'inzego zishinzwe iby'ubugenzuzi zemeza ko umuntu yakomeza kwivuza akoresheje imiti ihoraho yo kurwanya ACE n'iyo mu rwego rwa ARB.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku buryo bwitondewe n'abakoraga ubushakashatsi ku byerekeye indwara z'ubwonko, n'isubiramo ryabwo, byatangajwe ku itariki ya 11 Nyakanga 2012, bwagaragaje ko "gukoresha imiti itera ubwonko bw'ubwonko bw'ubwonko bw'ubwonko bw'ubwonko bw'ubwonko bw'ubwonko bw'ubwonko bwa ACE byagabanyije cyane ibyago byo kwandura ubwonko bwabwo ku kigero cya 34% ugereranyije n'ibikoresho by'ubugenzuzi".
Ikindi kandi, "gukoresha inhibition ya ACE byongeraga ibyago byo kurwara indwara ya PNIMONIYA mu barwayi bafite ibyago byo kurwara iyo ndwara, cyane cyane abarwayi barwaye indwara zo mu bwonko n'uburwayi bw'umutima.
Gukoresha inhibition ACE byanagaragajwe ko bigabanya urupfu ruva ku ndwara ya PN, nubwo byagize ingaruka nke ugereranyije n'ibyago by'indwara ya PN".
ACE2 yo mu bantu ikoreshwa mu kuvura (rhACE2) ni uburyo bushya bwo kuvura indwara z'ibihaha, kandi bisa n'ibikomeza ihumeka ry'ibihaha n'ihumeka ry'umwuka mu ngurube z'abafite indwara y'ihumeka ry'amaraso yatewe na lipoplysaccharide.
Igihe cy'igice cy'igice cy'igihe cy'icyunamo cy'ibihimba bya rhACE2 mu bantu ni amasaha agera kuri 10 ku gihe cy'akazi k'iminota 30 usibye igihe cy'ingaruka (igihe cy'igihe) cy'amasaha 24.
Hari ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko rhACE2 ishobora kuba umuti uhebuje ku barwayi batemera imiti ihoraho ya renin-angiotensin (RAS inhibitor) cyangwa ku barwayi bafite angiotensin II mu maraso y'abantu.
