Ku itariki ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple byatangaje ko bagiye gushyiraho uburyo bwo gushyigikira porogaramu zishingiye kuri Bluetooth mu buryo butaziguye muri sisitemu ya Android na iOS.
